BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260429T061800
DTEND:20260429T081800
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-1.195ft at 06:18\n-2.967ft at 08:18\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Morning starts off slow\, then a new blend of primary NW/WNW swell and sec
 ondary\, longer-period SSW swell gradually fill in during the day.  Over t
 he afternoon\, that sets up widespread waist-stomach- chest high range sur
 f\, while standouts see better sets\, largest late. \n\nLight/variable mor
 ning winds\, shift light+ WSW side shores mid day\, then offshore NW later
  afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
