BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260502T073600
DTEND:20260502T110000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.061ft at 07:36\n-2.956ft at 11:00\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Lingering mix of WNW and SSW swell starts the morning off in mainly thigh 
 to waist high+ waves\, then surf slowly tapers off during the afternoon as
  the old swell eases. Draining dawn patrol negative low tide\, then the in
 coming tide push gets an assist through mid morning. \n\nWinds looking lig
 ht/variable much of the morning\, light+ SW onshore mid day\, then turning
  offshore WNW for town spots over the afternoon. 
END:VEVENT
